data.description: Gorgeous home in Hallsville ISD with 4 bedrooms and 2 baths. Step in to the beautiful entry which leads to a large living area, high ceilings with lots of crown molding along with formal dining room.  The open floor plan is great for family gatherings. The kitchen has breakfast bar and breakfast room leading out to the covered patio. Large backyard with double and single gate. Lots of space in the oversized garage.  Plenty of room for a shop and pool.  This home is a must see!
